{"tid":1326101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家唔好失焦，亦請大家提提身邊嘅人","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:47:15.000Z","uid":217433,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7420bc129a325dfac1c1716d78d065fc0914bae8","tid":1326101,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"有無文宣組可以幫下手？<br />\n<br />\n自14號起，有沙田居民見到示威者嘅行為之後開始轉軚同情同支持警方，呢個轉變正正中咗政府下懷，將警察擺上枱同示威者對抗，對抗愈激烈就愈容易令中立嘅居民變淺藍，傾向支持警方。<br />\n<br />\n從來我地嘅示威活動唔係要推翻警權，亦都唔係要同警察對抗，但係只要有人個遊行焦點一放錯位，無論藍定黃，整個運動就會被騎劫。只要一失焦，所有事情都會重返14雨革嘅步伐，自6月所做嘅事就會付諸流水。<br />\n<br />\n所以有請文宣組，亦都懇請文宣組幫幫忙，將整個運動嘅焦點集中返5大訴求，甚至集中「反送中」。"},{"pid":"09bd009e1158b3e890ea18d5be0c7604a9c27d76","tid":1326101,"uid":161436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"adc423ac00f42d06142b26773d2c425a8585e6a6","tid":1326101,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"全力721"},{"pid":"9f011381ee0372c3d658c9f2df850e3c025db304","tid":1326101,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35d3047d94b1c7ffe0d1b1f9b04bc067a073d64","tid":1326101,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"521c4a834823d605691983eaea3f31918ec2af7b","tid":1326101,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a796a5bacffd3afd843d6e88aae210ec93a90e48","tid":1326101,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89fea0414e68aab507c2452583b73ee5594a435a","tid":1326101,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:40:10.000Z","msg":"失你老母焦 黑警 警權都係政府/5大訴求一部分 <br />\n大家請負評上一頁"},{"pid":"2a0cf7a0c6062558811d767582f38ec31d